HEADWORD: Gavelet
<hw>Gav"el*et</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From <er>Gavel</er>
tribute.]</ety> <fld>(O. Eng. Law)</fld> <def>An ancient special kind of
